---
title: Creamy Bacon & Green Bean Orecchiette with Parmesan & Parsley
description: Twirly-wirly pasta mixed in a creamy sauce is too good to be true. There are plenty of veggies hidden in amongst the
orecchiette to keep things fresh and green. For a bit of fun, throw in some diced bacon and you’ve cooked another
pasta-winning dinner.

